<rss version="2.0" xmlns:dc="http://purl.org/dc/elements/1.1/"><channel><title>中国新闻|今天的突破性故事|路透社</title><link>https://www.reuters.com/world/china/</link><description>Reuters.com是您最新的中国新闻报道和时事的在线来源</description><lastBuildDate>Tue, 28 Jan 2025 18:19:24 GMT</lastBuildDate><generator>rfeed v1.1.1</generator><docs>https://github.com/svpino/rfeed/blob/master/README.md</docs><item><title>消息人士称</title><link>https://www.reuters.com/business/northvolt-asks-shareholders-13-bln-next-two-years-sources-say-2025-01-28/</link><description>诺斯诺特（Northvolt）在本月的一次会议上要求100多名股东在未来两年内提供12.9亿美元，以帮助恢复破产的瑞典电池制造商的业务，两名熟悉此事的消息人士告诉路透社。</description><pubDate>Tue, 28 Jan 2025 16:48:26 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.reuters.com/business/northvolt-asks-shareholders-13-bln-next-two-years-sources-say-2025-01-28/</guid></item><item><title>特朗普的数字美元禁令使中国和欧洲的CBDC自由rein</title><link>https://www.reuters.com/markets/currencies/trumps-digital-dollar-ban-gives-china-europes-cbdcs-free-rein-2025-01-28/</link><description>观察家说，唐纳德·特朗普（Donald Trump）迅速宣布“数字美元”的举动使该领域的开放率使中国和欧洲将其已经很棒的中央银行数字货币（CBDC）原型制成全球标准制定者。</description><pubDate>Tue, 28 Jan 2025 15:40:17 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.reuters.com/markets/currencies/trumps-digital-dollar-ban-gives-china-europes-cbdcs-free-rein-2025-01-28/</guid></item><item><title>梅赛德斯 - 奔驰加入吉利（Geely）对欧盟对中国电动汽车关税的挑战</title><link>https://www.reuters.com/business/autos-transportation/mercedes-benz-joins-geelys-court-challenge-eu-tariffs-china-evs-2025-01-28/</link><description>公司发言人周二表示，梅赛德斯 - 奔驰已加入中国合资伙伴盖利（Geely）在欧盟法院（CJEU）（CJEU）对中国制造的电动汽车关税的法律挑战。</description><pubDate>Tue, 28 Jan 2025 15:36:23 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.reuters.com/business/autos-transportation/mercedes-benz-joins-geelys-court-challenge-eu-tariffs-china-evs-2025-01-28/</guid></item><item><title>原子科学家比以往任何时候都更接近“世界末日时钟”</title><link>https://www.reuters.com/world/atomic-scientists-adjust-doomsday-clock-closer-than-ever-midnight-2025-01-28/</link><description>原子科学家周二将其“世界末日时钟”移到了比以往更接近午夜的地方，理由是俄罗斯核威胁在其入侵乌克兰，其他世界热点的紧张局势，人工智能和气候变化的军事应用是全球灾难风险的因素。</description><pubDate>Tue, 28 Jan 2025 15:16:31 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.reuters.com/world/atomic-scientists-adjust-doomsday-clock-closer-than-ever-midnight-2025-01-28/</guid></item><item><title>美国科技库存，在深度触发的抛售后，美元反弹</title><link>https://www.reuters.com/markets/global-markets-global-markets-2025-01-28/</link><description>在低成本的中国AI模型摇摇欲坠的市场之后的第二天，全球技术股票恢复了一些基础，而交易员则从避风港货币中旋转回了美元。</description><pubDate>Tue, 28 Jan 2025 15:12:47 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.reuters.com/markets/global-markets-global-markets-2025-01-28/</guid></item><item><title>布里奇沃特（Bridgewater</title><link>https://www.reuters.com/technology/bridgewater-sees-short-term-correction-tech-stocks-bullish-deepseek-impact-2025-01-28/</link><description>对冲基金经理布里奇沃特（Bridgewater Associates）表示，中国初创公司DeepSeek推出了最新的人工智能（AI）模型，可能会导致许多科技公司的股价短期校正，但对该行业却是积极的。</description><pubDate>Tue, 28 Jan 2025 14:57:56 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.reuters.com/technology/bridgewater-sees-short-term-correction-tech-stocks-bullish-deepseek-impact-2025-01-28/</guid></item><item><title>独家：德意志银行关于中国合资局面关于控制的分歧的谈判。</title><link>https://www.reuters.com/business/finance/deutsche-bank-talks-china-jv-end-over-disagreement-control-sources-say-2025-01-28/</link><description>消息人士称，在德国公司抵制北京提高其股份的请求之后，德意志银行，其资产管理部门DWS和中国贷方邮政储蓄银行（PSBC）之间的会谈。</description><pubDate>Tue, 28 Jan 2025 13:54:46 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.reuters.com/business/finance/deutsche-bank-talks-china-jv-end-over-disagreement-control-sources-say-2025-01-28/</guid></item><item><title>认识DeepSeek的创始人：Liang Wenfeng可以颠覆AI行业</title><link>https://www.reuters.com/technology/deepseek-founder-liang-wenfeng-puts-focus-chinese-innovation-2025-01-28/</link><description>39岁的中国AI初创公司DeepSeek的创始人Liang Wenfeng在几周内成为中国科技行业的面貌，并希望克服美国实施的出口控制措施。</description><pubDate>Tue, 28 Jan 2025 12:16:49 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.reuters.com/technology/deepseek-founder-liang-wenfeng-puts-focus-chinese-innovation-2025-01-28/</guid></item><item><title>ASML在对Deepseek的希望和恐惧中报告第四季度的收入，特朗普</title><link>https://www.reuters.com/technology/asml-report-q4-earnings-amid-hopes-fears-over-deepseek-trump-2025-01-28/</link><description>投资者将寻求保证，尽管中国的DeepSeek抛售了ASML的AI依赖性增长前景，但由于在周三制造计算机芯片ASML报告收益的最大设备供应商中，尽管中国的DeepSeek抛售了抛售。</description><pubDate>Tue, 28 Jan 2025 11:38:26 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.reuters.com/technology/asml-report-q4-earnings-amid-hopes-fears-over-deepseek-trump-2025-01-28/</guid></item><item><title>独家：图像显示中国建立了巨大的融合研究机构，分析师说</title><link>https://www.reuters.com/world/china/images-show-china-building-huge-fusion-research-facility-analysts-say-2025-01-28/</link><description>两个分析组织的专家说，中国似乎正在西南城市米亚阳建立了一个大型激光融合研究中心，这一开发项目可以帮助核武器设计和探索发电。</description><pubDate>Tue, 28 Jan 2025 11:05:22 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.reuters.com/world/china/images-show-china-building-huge-fusion-research-facility-analysts-say-2025-01-28/</guid></item><item><title>大众首席执行官说，与中国合作伙伴谈论他们的欧洲扩张计划</title><link>https://www.reuters.com/business/autos-transportation/vw-ceo-confirms-talks-with-chinese-jv-partners-investing-german-plants-2025-01-28/</link><description>大众发言人周二表示，大众汽车公司的首席执行官已经与汽车制造商中国合资伙伴谈到了他们对在欧洲进行投资的兴趣，但不知道他们的任何具体决定。</description><pubDate>Tue, 28 Jan 2025 10:29:58 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.reuters.com/business/autos-transportation/vw-ceo-confirms-talks-with-chinese-jv-partners-investing-german-plants-2025-01-28/</guid></item><item><title>散户投资者在DeepSeek Rout购买了创纪录的NVIDIA股票</title><link>https://www.reuters.com/technology/retail-investors-bought-record-amount-nvidia-stock-deepseek-rout-2025-01-28/</link><description>零售投资者周一购买了创纪录的NVIDIA股票，此前中国初创公司DeepSeek的低成本人工智能模型的担忧剥夺了其股票17％的折扣，或者从其市值中剥离了5930亿美元。</description><pubDate>Tue, 28 Jan 2025 10:19:23 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.reuters.com/technology/retail-investors-bought-record-amount-nvidia-stock-deepseek-rout-2025-01-28/</guid></item><item><title>阿里巴巴支持的公司购买了12％的意大利豪华运动鞋制造商Golden Goose</title><link>https://www.reuters.com/markets/deals/alibabas-tsai-backed-firm-buys-12-italian-luxury-sneaker-maker-golden-goose-2025-01-28/</link><description>位于阿里巴巴联合创始人乔·泰（Joe Tsai）支持的一家基于香港的投资公司Blue Pool已购买了意大利豪华运动鞋制造商Golden Goose的12％股份。</description><pubDate>Tue, 28 Jan 2025 09:03:39 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.reuters.com/markets/deals/alibabas-tsai-backed-firm-buys-12-italian-luxury-sneaker-maker-golden-goose-2025-01-28/</guid></item><item><title>俄罗斯石油贸易到中国，随着制裁推动运输费用，印度摊位</title><link>https://www.reuters.com/markets/commodities/russia-oil-trade-china-india-stalls-sanctions-drive-up-shipping-costs-2025-01-28/</link><description>根据交易员和运输数据的数据，在亚洲顶级买家中加载俄罗斯石油的贸易已成为买卖双方之间在中国出现的巨大价格差距。</description><pubDate>Tue, 28 Jan 2025 06:14:14 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.reuters.com/markets/commodities/russia-oil-trade-china-india-stalls-sanctions-drive-up-shipping-costs-2025-01-28/</guid></item><item><title>泰国否认中国想要的虐待被拘留的赌博大亨</title><link>https://www.reuters.com/world/asia-pacific/thailand-denies-mistreating-detained-gambling-tycoon-wanted-by-china-2025-01-28/</link><description>泰国司法部长周二表示，泰国否认滥用被判入狱的赌博大亨，以他在东南亚进行非法在线赌博业务的指控，违反了引渡到中国的指控。</description><pubDate>Tue, 28 Jan 2025 05:52:19 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.reuters.com/world/asia-pacific/thailand-denies-mistreating-detained-gambling-tycoon-wanted-by-china-2025-01-28/</guid></item></channel></rss>